    "Choose separate sounds for tasks and events, preview them before selecting, or import your own audio. Imported sounds are copied into Hot Cross Buns so playback keeps working even if the original file moves.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ms": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pilih bunyi yang berasingan untuk tugasan dan acara, pratontonnya sebelum memilih, atau import audio anda sendiri. Bunyi yang diimport disalin ke dalam Hot Cross Buns supaya main balik terus berfungsi walaupun fail asal bergerak."
          }
        },
        "ta": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "பணிகள் மற்றும் நிகழ்வுகளுக்கான தனி ஒலிகளைத் தேர்வுசெய்யவும், அவற்றைத் தேர்ந்தெடுப்பதற்கு முன் முன்னோட்டமிடவும் அல்லது உங்கள் சொந்த ஆடியோவை இறக்குமதி செய்யவும். இறக்குமதி செய்யப்பட்ட ஒலிகள் ஹாட் கிராஸ் பன்ஸில் நகலெடுக்கப்படுகின்றன, எனவே அசல் கோப்பு நகர்ந்தாலும் பிளேபேக் வேலை செய்யும்."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "为任务和事件选择单独的声音，在选择之前预览它们，或导入您自己的音频。导入的声音会复制到 Hot Cross Buns 中，因此即使原始文件移动，播放也能继续进行。"
          }
        },
        "id": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Choose separate sounds for tasks and events, preview them before selecting, or import your own audio. Imported sounds are copied into Hot Cross Buns so playback keeps working even if the original file moves."
          }
        },
        "vi": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Choose separate sounds for tasks and events, preview them before selecting, or import your own audio. Imported sounds are copied into Hot Cross Buns so playback keeps working even if the original file moves."
          }
        },
        "th": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Choose separate sounds for tasks and events, preview them before selecting, or import your own audio. Imported sounds are copied into Hot Cross Buns so playback keeps working even if the original file moves."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Choose separate sounds for tasks and events, preview them before selecting, or import your own audio. Imported sounds are copied into Hot Cross Buns so playback keeps working even if the original file moves."
          }
        },
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Choose separate sounds for tasks and events, preview them before selecting, or import your own audio. Imported sounds are copied into Hot Cross Buns so playback keeps working even if the original file moves."
          }
